00:02:01.380 --> 00:02:02.480
OK, this is yours.

00:02:02.480 --> 00:02:04.050
Thank you.

00:02:04.050 --> 00:02:05.790
I went to my grandmother.

00:02:05.790 --> 00:02:07.620
She gave me her recipes.

00:02:07.620 --> 00:02:09.840
She told me to keep trying them, perfect them.

00:02:09.840 --> 00:02:12.210
So I perfected the recipes.

00:02:12.210 --> 00:02:16.620
I started out baking in my grandmother's kitchen.

00:02:16.620 --> 00:02:18.240
The oven was small.

00:02:18.240 --> 00:02:19.500
The kitchen was small.

00:02:19.500 --> 00:02:22.800
And I was receiving overwhelming orders.

00:02:22.800 --> 00:02:24.810
It was like a no-brainer to say, you

00:02:24.810 --> 00:02:26.310
