00:02:47.730 --> 00:02:49.500
I answered the questions.

00:02:49.500 --> 00:02:52.350
They finally said, yeah, you can try it out.

00:02:52.350 --> 00:02:53.460
One banana pudding.

00:02:53.460 --> 00:02:55.350
So I tried it out.

00:02:55.350 --> 00:02:57.030
And two pineapple coconuts.

00:02:57.030 --> 00:02:59.970
I was told that this cake store wouldn't do well.

00:02:59.970 --> 00:03:03.120
There wasn't many businesses in this area.

00:03:03.120 --> 00:03:04.260
Enjoy.

00:03:04.260 --> 00:03:08.490
We've stuck it out and that was March 2012.

00:03:08.490 --> 00:03:11.340
And we're here nine years later.

00:03:11.340 --> 00:03:13.680
Success comes to those who stick with it.

00:03:13.680 --> 00:03:14.940
I do want the peach cobbler.

00:03:14.940 --> 00:03:16.320
That's what I came here for.

00:03:16.320 --> 00:03:20.620
We've become a beacon of light to the community.

00:03:20.620 --> 00:03:21.120
Oh, man.

00:03:21.120 --> 00:03:22.680
